title: 1907 Colfax #101 Huge 2-bdrm! $1200!!
posting_body: ["This is a wonderful 1960's era property, one block off Hennepin.", 'Walking distance from Lake of the Isles and a short bike ride to beautiful Bde Maka Ska!', 'Live at the crossroads of the city, a ten minute drive from wherever you want to be!', 'This 2-bedroom apartment is super-spacious with beautiful hardwood floors though-out!', 'Beautiful wood cabinets, eat-in dining area, and lots of closet space.', 'Ceiling fan and built in air conditioner for your comfort.', "Located in the Lowry Hill area of Uptown, you will have easy access to all the area's amenities, plus be close by the wonderful lakes of south Minneapolis.", 'RENTAL FEATURES', '_________________________________________________________________________________', 'Great Kitchen', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Living Room', 'Dining Room', 'Closets', 'Gas Stove / Oven', 'Refrigerator', 'Cable-ready', 'Fiber Optic Available', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', '_________________________________________________________________________________', 'Controlled access', 'Bus line quick walk away', 'Professionally managed', 'LEASE TERMS', '________________________________________________________________________________', 'Managed and maintained by Hornig Companies, Inc.', 'Apply online at <URL>', '6 and 9 month leases available for an additional fee.', '*images may not be of actual unit, but representative.']
